Sure, here are some example sentences using the Serbian word "ulje" (*oil*) in different forms and positions:

1. *Ulje* je važan sastojak u kuvanju. (*Oil* is an important ingredient in cooking.) 
2. Naš auto troši mnogo *ulja*. (Our car consumes a lot of *oil*.)
3. Ovo jelo možete napraviti i bez *ulja*. (You can make this dish without *oil* too.)
4. Moram da kupim novu bočicu *ulja*. (I need to buy a new bottle of *oil*.)
5. *Ulje* iz semena grožđa koristi se u kozmetici. (*Grape seed oil* is used in cosmetics.)
6. Kada zagrejete *ulje*, dodajte luk. (When you heat up *oil*, add onion.)
7. Domaće *ulje* je ukusnije od kupovnog. (Homemade *oil* is tastier than store-bought.)
8. Često koristim maslinovo *ulje* u salatama. (I often use olive *oil* in salads.)

I hope these examples help!